com.vmware.vcenter.namespace_management.supervisor_services

Interface ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClusterSupervisorServices
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClusterSupervisorServicesStub

    public interface ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes
    The ClusterSupervisorServices interface provides methods to manage a Supervisor Service on the vSphere Supervisors. This interface was added in vSphere API 7.0.3.0.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes.ConfigStatus
      The ConfigStatus enumeration class describes the status of reaching the desired state configuration for the Supervisor Service.
      static class  ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes.CreateSpec
      The CreateSpec class provides a specification required to create a Supervisor Service on a vSphere Supervisor.
      static class  ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes.Info
      The Info class contains the detailed information about a Supervisor Service on the vSphere Supervisor.
      static class  ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes.Message
      The Message class contains the information about the Supervisor Service configuration on a vSphere Supervisor.
      static class  ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes.SetSpec
      The SetSpec class provides a specification required to set a new configuration on a Supervisor Service in a vSphere Supervisor.
      static class  ClusterSupervisorServicesTypes.Summary
      The Summary class contains the basic information about a Supervisor Service on the vSphere Supervisor.
